{"word":"G4306 - προνοέω - pronoéō - pron-o-eh'-o - Provide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προνοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pronoéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pron-o-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Provide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நாடு, விசாரி"},{"paragraph":"1. to perceive before, foresee"},{"paragraph":"2. to provide, think of beforehand"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G3539 - νοιέω - noiéō - noy-eh'-o/3539\">G3539</a>; to <i>consider in advance</i>, that is, <i>look</i> out for <i>beforehand</i> (active voice by way of <i>maintenance</i> for others; middle voice by way of <i>circumspection</i> for oneself): - provide (for).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1270/1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271/1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425/1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771/1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132/2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133/2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657/2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279/279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340/3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539/3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540/3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559/3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563/3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306/4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307/4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453/453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454/454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282/5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283/5283\">G5283</a>"}]}